    <briefdescription>
<para>A traits struct for accessing type aliases of an interpolation builder. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The primary template delegates to the builder&apos;s own type aliases, so any class that defines them directly (e.g. <ref refid="classIdentityInterpolationBuilder" kindref="compound">IdentityInterpolationBuilder</ref>, SplineBuilder1D) satisfies the InterpolationBuilder concept without specialisation.</para>
<para>Specialise this struct to adapt external builders whose alias names differ from the convention (e.g. ddc::SplineBuilder).</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Builder</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The interpolation builder type. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
